title: Release v0.4.0
message:
Release v0.4.0

Merge branch '2.23-legacy'

title: New features:
message:
New features:
- Make TEI attribute number shown variable depending on the screen (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-128)
- Add a link to add entities through relationships (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-105)
- Screen Spacing On Register Relationship Page (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-104)
- Tracker Dashboard Headings (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-94)
- Delete Events in Android Tracker Capture (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-127)

Bugfixing:
- Android allows to change the enrollment date (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-129)
- Unique attributes not respected on the Tracker Capture Android App (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-126, https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-125)
- TC doesn’t work with eRegistry server (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-115, https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-84)
- Sync Refactor (https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-103, https://jira.dhis2.org/browse/ACA-102)
